              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": "fill_container",
              "gap": 32,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "0VGIH",
                  "name": "Story 1 - Child",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#FFFFFF15",
                  "cornerRadius": 16,
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "padding": [
                    24,
                    20
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "O5c0L",
                      "name": "s1period",
                      "fill": "$color-accent",
                      "content": "2004 — 2019",
                      "fontFamily": "Rubik Mono One",
                      "fontSize": 14
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "jUMPI",
                      "name": "s1title",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                      "content": "When I was a child",
                      "lineHeight": 1.2,
                      "fontFamily": "Rubik Mono One",
                      "fontSize": 18
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "rnq8L",
                      "name": "s1desc",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFFCC",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "I was always curious about the world around me. I loved drawing, tinkering, and most of my questions began with \"how\" or \"why\". When I got my first video game console, something clicked.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Ledger",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "rectangle",
                      "cornerRadius": 2,
                      "id": "g0SXR",
                      "name": "Progress Bar",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFF40",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "height": 3
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "PSF0p",
                  "name": "Story 2 - Teen",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#FFFFFF15",
                  "cornerRadius": 16,
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "padding": [
                    24,
                    20
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "QyaiH",
                      "name": "s2period",
                      "fill": "$color-accent",
                      "content": "2019 — 2025",
                      "fontFamily": "Rubik Mono One",
                      "fontSize": 14
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "k3GVg",
                      "name": "s2title",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                      "content": "Reaching my teenage years",
                      "lineHeight": 1.2,
                      "fontFamily": "Rubik Mono One",
                      "fontSize": 18
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "o3vcD",
                      "name": "s2desc",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFFCC",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "I left my parents' home to live in the mountains and start an apprenticeship in computer science. There, I learned systems, networking, and the basics of software development.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Ledger",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "rectangle",
                      "cornerRadius": 2,
                      "id": "mW6ty",
                      "name": "Progress Bar",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "height": 3
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "zuRDy",
                  "name": "Story 3 - Today",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#FFFFFF15",
                  "cornerRadius": 16,
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "padding": [
                    24,
                    20
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "itfqb",
                      "name": "s3period",
                      "fill": "$color-accent",
                      "content": "2025 — Today",
                      "fontFamily": "Rubik Mono One",
                      "fontSize": 14
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "a1Isi",
                      "name": "s3title",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                      "content": "Today",
                      "lineHeight": 1.2,
                      "fontFamily": "Rubik Mono One",
                      "fontSize": 18
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "kFEaH",
                      "name": "s3desc",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFFCC",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "I'm proud of the journey I've taken so far, but my eyes are still on tomorrow. I keep learning in specific fields to satisfy my curiosity, and I often dive into ambitious projects.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Ledger",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "rectangle",
                      "cornerRadius": 2,
                      "id": "Q1nDJ",
                      "name": "Progress Bar",
                      "fill": "#FFFFFF60",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "height": 3
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
