                  "fill": "#FFFFFFCC",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Sprunk-engine is an open-source web game engine (available on npm) that I developed with some friends. We wanted a challenging, architecture-focused project, so we built a game engine with almost no external libraries. It lets developers create 2D browser games.",
